contentrichtext.text: '''Fontenoy''' ({{IPA-fr|fɔ̃tənwa}}) may refer to: *[[Battle of Fontenoy (1745)]] *[[Battle of Fontenay (841)]] *[[Fontenoy (novel)]] by Liam Mac Cóil ==People== *[[Maud Fontenoy]], a French sailor ==Places== Belgium: *Fontenoy, a village in the municipality of [[Antoing]], Belgium Several [[Commune in France|commune]]s in [[France]]: *[[Fontenoy, Aisne|Fontenoy]], in the [[Aisne]] ''[[département in France|département]]'' *[[Fontenoy, Yonne|Fontenoy]], in the [[Yonne]] ''département'' *[[Fontenoy-la-Joûte]], in the [[Meurthe-et-Moselle]] ''département'' (a [[book town]]) *[[Fontenoy-le-Château]], in the [[Vosges]] ''département'' *[[Fontenoy-sur-Moselle]], in the [[Meurthe-et-Moselle]] ''département'' Australia: *[[Fontenoy, New South Wales|Fontenoy]],a property owned by the Moloney family in Junee, New South Wales United States: *[[Fontenoy, Wisconsin|Fontenoy]], an unincorporated community in Brown County, Wisconsin ==See also== *[[Fontenay (disambiguation)]] {{disambig}}
